mount NFS mountpoint on server-:
1. Create Mount Point
    sudo mkdir -p /mnt/nfs
2. Mount NFS
    sudo mount -t nfs 10.0.1.10:/export/data /mnt/nfs
3. Verify
    df -Th

4. Permanent Mount (IMPORTANT)
    1. open file
      sudo vi /etc/fstab
    2. add 10.0.1.10:/export/data   /mnt/nfs   nfs   defaults,nofail,_netdev   0 0
    3. test using sudo mount -a
in NFS mounting Port 2049 should be open 




