EFS mounting-:
1. sudo yum install -y nfs-utils
2.  sudo mkdir /efs
3. sudo mount -t nfs4 -o nfsvers=4.1 fs-06bf01a2a0d18fe51.efs.us-east-1.amazonaws.com:/ /efs
4. df -Th    ==== to check mounted or not
5. sudo vi /etc/fstab
6. add fs-06bf01a2a0d18fe51.efs.us-east-1.amazonaws.com:/   /efs   nfs4   _netdev,noresvport,nfsvers=4.1   0 0
7. test using sudo mount -a
8. 

unmount EFS-:
sudo umount /efs or sudo umount -l /efs === for force unmount

